Class Events

java.lang.Object
Events
All Implemented Interfaces:
Concert, Other, Show
public class Events extends Object implements Concert, Show, Other
This class encompasses an event that is specific to a festival_run object. This class is implemented using the Strategy design pattern since we have three different types of Events that can occur, but only one at a time.
